rop\" width=\"1200\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-foreground/68 via-foreground/10 to-transparent\"></div><div class=\"experience-panel\"><p class=\"mb-3 font-sans text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.24em] opacity-75\">Forest hour</p><h3 class=\"font-heading text-[clamp(2rem,4vw,4.8rem)] leading-[0.88] tracking-[-0.045em]\">Luxury Safaris</h3><p class=\"mt-4 max-w-md font-sans text-sm leading-relaxed opacity-80\">Dawn and dusk drives in Ranthambore with naturalists who read the forest by sound, dust, and pause.</p></div></article><article class=\"experience-card group\"><img alt=\"Wellness Retreats\" class=\"absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 ease-out group-hover:scale-105\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://images.pexels.com/photos/3225528/pexels-photo-3225528.jpeg?auto=compress&amp;cs=tinysrgb&amp;w=1200\" width=\"1200\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-foreground/68 via-foreground/10 to-transparent\"></div><div class=\"experience-panel\"><p class=\"mb-3 font-sans text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.24em] opacity-75\">Stillness</p><h3 class=\"font-heading text-[clamp(2rem,4vw,4.8rem)] leading-[0.88] tracking-[-0.045em]\">Wellness Retreats</h3><p class=\"mt-4 max-w-md font-sans text-sm leading-relaxed opacity-80\">Ayurvedic therapies, yoga, and lake-facing quiet in palace settings designed for recovery rather than performance.</p></div></article></div>","computedStyles":{"font-family":"\"Space Grotesk Variable\", sans-serif","font-size":"16px","font-weight":"400","line-height":"24px","color":"oklch(0.153 0.006 107.1)","background":"none","background-color":"rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)","padding":"0px","margin":"0px","display":"grid","position":"static","gap":"32px","border-radius":"0px","box-shadow":"none"},"cssCustomProperties":{"--background":"oklch(1 0 0)","--foreground":"oklch(0.153 0.006 107.1)","--card":"oklch(1 0 0)","--card-foreground":"oklch(0.153 0.006 107.1)","--popover":"oklch(1 0 0)","--popover-f